{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"ida903df8e-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1706"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1706"},"text":"§ 1706.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Government performance of certain acquisition functions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida903df8f-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1706/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Goal","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"It shall be the goal of the Department of Defense and each of the military departments to ensure that, for each major defense acquisition program (as defined in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s4201"},"text":"section 4201 of this title","children":[],"tail":"), each acquisition program that is estimated by the Secretary of Defense to require an eventual total expenditure greater than the amount described in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s4201/a/2"},"text":"section 4201(a)(2) of this title","children":[],"tail":", and any other acquisition program identified by the Secretary, each of the following positions is performed by a properly qualified member of the armed forces or full-time employee of the Department of Defense:"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida903df90-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1706/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Portfolio acquisition executive.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida903df91-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1706/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Deputy portfolio acquisition executive.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida903df92-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1706/a/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Program manager.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida903df93-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1706/a/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Deputy program manager.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida903df94-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1706/a/5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5"},"text":"(5)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Senior contracting official.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida903df95-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1706/a/6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6"},"text":"(6)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Chief developmental tester.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida903df96-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1706/a/7"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"7"},"text":"(7)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Program lead product support manager.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida903df97-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1706/a/8"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"8"},"text":"(8)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","at